{"sn22.106:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 22.106 ","sn22.106:0.2":"11. Antavagga ","sn22.106:0.3":"Parinneyyasutta ","sn22.106:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn22.106:1.2":"“Parinneyye ca, bhikkhave, dhamme desessami parinnanca parinnatavinca puggalam. ","sn22.106:1.3":"Tam sunatha. ","sn22.106:1.4":"Katame ca, bhikkhave, parinneyya dhamma? ","sn22.106:1.5":"Rupam, bhikkhave, parinneyyo dhammo. ","sn22.106:1.6":"Vedana …pe… ","sn22.106:1.7":"sanna … ","sn22.106:1.8":"sankhara … ","sn22.106:1.9":"vinnanam parinneyyo dhammo. ","sn22.106:1.10":"Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, parinneyya dhamma. ","sn22.106:1.11":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, parinna? ","sn22.106:1.12":"Ragakkhayo, dosakkhayo, mohakkhayo—","sn22.106:1.13":"ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, parinna. ","sn22.106:1.14":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, parinnatavi puggalo? ","sn22.106:1.15":"Arahatissa vacaniyam. ","sn22.106:1.16":"Yvayam ayasma evamnamo evangotto—","sn22.106:1.17":"ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, parinnatavi puggalo”ti. ","sn22.106:1.18":"Catuttham. "}